msg: In preparation for removing the last entry write operations, make
svn_wc__db_base_add_absent_node() store the absent marker in the
parent stub even if there is a directory. Also add an helper to
read some base information from a parent working copy if the
real data is obstructed by a new working copy.

is a directory. (In most use cases there is only a stub)
